-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-10T18:05:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/mcalinden-says-small-caps-may-lead-market-to-new-highs-video-.html
Joseph McAlinden, chief investment 
officer at Catalpa Capital LLC, talks about the outlook for 
global equity markets, his investment strategy and expectations 
for third-quarter U.S. corporate earnings.  He speaks with Pimm Fox on Bloomberg Television's 
"Surveillance Midday." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:26
 